2 Requirements
**************

   • Emacs 28.1 or later (for ‘json-parse-string’ and ‘when-let*’ with
     bindings).
   • The built-in ‘url’, ‘json’, ‘dom’, and ‘seq’ libraries (all shipped
     with Emacs).
   • zotra (https://github.com/mpedramfar/zotra) (optional)--only needed
     for ‘bib-zotra-add-entry-from-title’.


